  "algorithm_summary": "Two T2D case algorithms are provided: preferred (t2d_dprism_ehr_plus_1) includes self-reported survey data, alternative (t2d_dprism_ehr_1) uses EHR only. Cases require: 1) Exclusion of T1D diagnoses, 2) T2D ICD codes with diabetes medications (insulin requires additional non-insulin medication or \u22652 T2D diagnoses), or 3) T2D ICD without medications requires abnormal glucose/HbA1c, or 4) Non-insulin diabetes medications with abnormal labs. Controls require: \u22651 healthcare visit, \u22651 glucose measurement, no abnormal glucose/HbA1c values, no diabetes diagnoses/medications, and no related conditions (prediabetes, glycosuria). Age filter \u226525 years applies to both cases and controls.",
